#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_short_boxed: Black"
msgstr "5-短络腮胡：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_short_boxed: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid ""
"You have a black moustache and a short beard with trimmed sides.  Thin "
"patches connect them both, forming a 'box' around the lips, thus the name."
msgstr "你有一撮黑色的小胡子和两侧修剪整齐的短络腮胡。稀疏的毛发将两者连接起来，在嘴唇周围形成一个“方框”，因此得名。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_goatee: Black"
msgstr "5-山羊胡：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_goatee: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "You have a short black beard at the tip of your chin."
msgstr "你的下巴尖上有一撮黑色的短山羊胡。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_full: Black"
msgstr "5-全脸胡：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_full: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid ""
"You have a black moustache and a long beard, both formed by allowing free "
"growth of hair, with no particular styling."
msgstr "你有一撮黑色的小胡子和长长的络腮胡，两者都是任由毛发自由生长而成，没有特别的造型。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_chevron: Black"
msgstr "5-八字胡：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_chevron: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "You have a black moustache that covers your entire top lip."
msgstr "你有一撮覆盖整个上唇的黑色八字胡。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_neckbeard: Black"
msgstr "5-颈须：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_neckbeard: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid ""
"You have a black beard formed from hair grown on neck below the chin line.  "
"No moustache included."
msgstr "你有一撮由下巴线以下颈部生长的毛发形成的黑色颈须。不包括小胡子。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_moustache: Black"
msgstr "5-胡须_小胡子：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_moustache: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid ""
"You have a black moustache with shortened ends, that covers only the skin "
"above your upper lip."
msgstr "你有一副黑色的小胡子，末端修剪得较短，仅覆盖上唇上方的皮肤。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_royale: Black"
msgstr "5-胡须_皇家式：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_royale: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid ""
"You have a black moustache and a short beard forming a patch under your "
"lips."
msgstr "你有一副黑色的小胡子和一小撮短胡须，在下唇下方形成一块胡须区域。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_soul_patch: Black"
msgstr "5-胡须_灵魂贴片：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_soul_patch: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid ""
"You have a little bit of black hair in the dip under your lower lip, and no "
"other facial hair whatsoever."
msgstr "你在下唇下方的凹陷处有一小撮黑色毛发，除此之外没有任何其他面部毛发。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_chin_strap: Black"
msgstr "5-胡须_下巴带：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_chin_strap: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
